---
title: Slow-Cooked Peppercorn Pork Meatballs with Garlic Rice & Chives
description: Our Slow Cook recipes are perfect for those cold nights - switch on your oven and get ready to cook low and slow to pack maximum flavour. Juicy little pork balls braised in a herb finish with an array of veggies are as delicious as they look, trust us. Add a punch to the meal with a peppercorn sauce and garlic infused rice. Meatballs are always a fun dinner options, there’s just so much flavour packed into
a single bite!

